content.rendered: Pasang DVR dari Infinity HDTVI DVR TDV-5304/5308/5316-H1 untuk kebutuhan kamera pengawas. Anda dapat memantau kegiatan / aktivitas sehari-hari dengan jarak jauh secara real time. Jenis kamera Infinity type HDTVI DVR TDV-5304/5308/5316-H1 memiliki spesifikasiTurbo HD DVR 04/08/16 ch Features Connectable to HDTVI, AHD, HDCVI and analog cameras Up to 1-ch 2MP IP cameras input for infinity TDV-5304-H1 3-ch 2MP IP cameras input for infinity TDV-5308/5316-H1 Long distance transmission over UTP and coaxial cable compression and recording One key enable H.264+ compression to improve encoding efficiency by up to 50% and reduce data storage costs Full channel recording up to 1080p resolution
